          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Three-body He-3 photodisintegration was  measured  in",
                " the  photon  energy  range  Eg = 145 - 425 MeV.  The",
                " total cross section for photon absorption on the  np",
                " pairs   in   He-3,   sig(He-3(g,np)p-spectator),  is",
                " reported here for the first time.  The Eg-dependence",
                " of  the  sigma  is  found  to scale to that of sigma",
                " (He-2(g,np)),  and their ratio  is determined to  be",
                " 1.24(0.26)."
              ]
            }
          ],
